    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071247_3_439-494",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "439-494",
      "markText": "文明偏在外，属物质方面。文化偏在内，属精神方面。故文明可以向外传播与接受，文化则必由其群体内部精神累积而产生。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071247&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=439&rangeEnd=494",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fb32210813ab8254g017435?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=439&rangeEnd=494"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071247_3_2492-2566",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2492-2566",
      "markText": "然则中国之改进，使其变为一崭新的大型农国而依然保有其深度之安足感，实不仅为中国一国之幸，抑于全世界人类文化前程以及举世渴望之和平，必可有绝大之贡献。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071247&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2492&rangeEnd=2566",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fb32210813ab8254g017435?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2492&rangeEnd=2566"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071247_7_4417-4503",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4417-4503",
      "markText": "惟其常向外看，认为有两体对立，所以特別注意在空间的“扩张”，以及“权力”和“征服”上。惟其常向内看，认为只有一体浑然，所以特别注意到时间的“绵延”以及“生长”和“根本”上。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071247&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4417&rangeEnd=4503",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fb32210813ab8254g017435?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4417&rangeEnd=4503"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071247_9_1932-2010",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1932-2010",
      "markText": "中国人则较为倾向“身心一致”的观念，并不信有灵肉对立。他看世界，亦不认为对我而超然独立，他依然不是向外看，而是向内看。他认为我与世界还是息息相通，融为一体。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071247&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1932&rangeEnd=2010",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fb32210813ab8254g017435?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1932&rangeEnd=2010"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300071247_3_926-964",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "926-964",
      "markText": "各地文化精神之不同，穷其根源，最先还是由于自然环境有分别，而影响其生活方式。",
      "totalCount": 132,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300071247&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=926&rangeEnd=964",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2fb32210813ab8254g017435?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=926&rangeEnd=964"
    },
